messages.content: Kindly share your contact will call you.

Hi , 

I hope this message finds you well! My name is Architha Kurreli, and I am reaching out on behalf of 8 Views. We are a 100 member marketing company that has worked with 250+ brands in the last 8 years.

We've been looking at your content and are impressed with the authentic connection you have with your audience.

We are currently exploring potential collaborations with influential voices like yours to drive value for the brands we manage which will be mutually beneficial.

Before we delve deeper into the specifics, we'd love to learn more about your collaboration costs which will help us practically plan which brand could be suitable.

It would be great if you could help us with your contact number to discuss further.

Thanks & Regards 
Architha Kurreli 
8 Views
